OL,3,CCouncil reveal plans to shut public
OL,4,Ctoilets to save money
OL,6,FAll the public toilets in Denbighshire
OL,7,Fwill close if the council's cost-
OL,8,Fcutting plans are approved later this
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe council argues it faces
OL,12,F"unprecedented" financial challenges,
OL,13,Fand hopes if the plans to shut public
OL,14,Fconveniences go ahead it will save
OL,15,Fmore than #200,000.
OL,17,FHowever, the plans have been heavily
OL,18,Fcriticised for the impact it could
OL,19,Fhave on tourists, the elderly and
OL,20,Fdisabled people.
