OL,3,CCouncil reveal plans to shut public
OL,4,Ctoilets to save money
OL,6,FAs part of the plans, councillors hope
OL,7,Fsmaller city, town & community
OL,8,Fcouncils will be able to foot the bill
OL,9,Fand keep the facilities open.
OL,11,FIt's also been suggested that local
OL,12,Fbusinesses could open up their
OL,13,Ftoilets, for a #500 payment.
OL,15,FAs councils budgets get squeezed,
OL,16,Fcouncil leaders are considering
OL,17,Fdifferent ways to cut back on spending.
