OL,3,CCouncil reveal plans to shut public
OL,4,Ctoilets to save money
OL,6,FDenbighshire Council's newest plans
OL,7,Fcould see the closure of all their
OL,8,Fpublic toilets, saving it more than
OL,9,F#300,000.
OL,11,FProviding public conveniences is not a
OL,12,Fstatutory requirement for local
OL,13,Fauthorities, so Denbighshire council
OL,14,Fargue that many other councils have
OL,15,F"reduced or ceased this service many
OL,16,Fyears ago".
