OL,3,CCouncil reveal plans to shut public
OL,4,Ctoilets to save money
OL,6,FThe proposal has been met with heavy
OL,7,Fcriticism from people who are
OL,8,Fconcerned about the impact toilet
OL,9,Fclosures will have on tourist, the
OL,10,Felderly and disabled people.
OL,12,FGareth Parsons, the chair of Wales
OL,13,FSenior Forum, said that the absence of
OL,14,Ftoilets causes "panic, desperation, or
OL,15,Fdistress" for elderly people.
OL,17,FMr Parsons added, "people aren't going
OL,18,Fto go into town if they haven't got
OL,19,Faccess to a toilet.
