OL,3,CCouncil reveal plans to shut public
OL,4,Ctoilets to save money
OL,6,F"Older people would be worried about
OL,7,Fgoing into a town if there isn't a
OL,8,Ftoilet - certainly in an unfamiliar
OL,9,Farea".
OL,11,FOn the streets of Rhyl, many people
OL,12,Fshare these concerns. One man told ITV
OL,13,FWales, "it would be a disgrace - there
OL,14,Fshould always be loos about".
OL,16,FAnother shopper said, "I think it is
OL,17,Fdisgusting, it's not a good idea at
OL,18,Fall. People with children need to go
OL,19,Fwhen they need to go!
