OL,4,Ctoilets to save money
OL,6,F"We hope, in areas where the provision
OL,7,Fof Public Conveniences is considered
OL,8,Fto be absolutely essential, that City,
OL,9,FTown & Community Councils may have the
OL,10,Fability and appetite to provide that
OL,11,Fservice instead."
OL,13,FNothing has been decided yet, but the
OL,14,Fcouncil's cabinet will reach its final
OL,15,Fdecision later this year.
